<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee33c6fa-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s495"><num value="495">§ 495.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated, out of any moneys in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, such sums as may be necessary after the fiscal year beginning <date date="1927-07-01">July 1, 1927</date> to carry out the purposes of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee33c6fb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1927-03-03/ch309/s3">Mar. 3, 1927, ch. 309, § 3</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/44/1355">44 Stat. 1355</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idee33c6fc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idee33c6fd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idee33c6fe-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section constitutes part of section 3 of act <date date="1927-03-03">Mar. 3, 1927</date>. Remainder of section 3 is classified to sections 494 and 496 of this title.</p>
</note>
</notes>
